{
  "stem": "14060.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a systematic program of-- to submit the Jews to all sorts of economic and other indignities, and make their life more difficult gradually.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't a matter which-- that you woke up one morning and suddenly you couldn't go on the street.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You could carry on your life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You were fooled into a security, which really was getting worse by months, by years.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you got mentally into a frame of mind that you didn't consider it's terrible.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was just another event.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so it went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Today when I look back on it, I realize how naive the whole mentality was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't even say that anybody who would've-- be-- let it be American Jews or in England, would have been put to the same that they would have acted very differently, because what should you do?",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You take a gun out?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Your throw a hand grenade?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was no reason for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So there were times when Jews were oppressed in countries.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there came a time when things became better.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You did not realize that this was a systematic [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] way, which led eventually to the Final Solution.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And obviously-- however clever and however clear it was, obviously there were people-- I remember in our town, in 1937, the family called-- he was a timber merchant.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He lived in our street, emigrated to Palestine, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were some families who rightly, correctly, anticipated the worst.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they were in such minority that I think in our community of a few hundred families, maybe two or three families left.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It could have been partly influenced by the fact that it was difficult to get in.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
